    "Unknown": "). \u2014 The false teachers at Galatia charged Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]` with duplicity. They said in one place Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]` preaches circumcision (on one occasion he had Timothy circumcised as a matter of expediency), and in another place he opposes it. Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]` had Timothy circumcised (Acts 16:3) in hopes of being conciliatory to the Jews (It didn\u2019t work.), not to make Timothy righteous or more spiritual. The fact is, those who oppose the gospel of God\u2019s free, sovereign, absolute grace in Christ, claiming to be promoters of righteousness, never hesitate to slander any who preach free grace, hurling accusations against them that they know are not true. Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]`\u2019s response is simple and pointed. He asks, \u201cIf I preach circumcision (law obedience) why do your legalistic teachers relentlessly oppose me?\u201d They opposed him because the cross of Christ is now, ever has been, and ever will be an offense to work-mongers. Lost religious people do not object to the teaching that Christ is the Son of God, the Savior of sinners, the Lord our Righteousness, and our sin-atoning Substitute. They only object to that which offends their own self-righteousness \u2014 the plain revelation of the gospel that Christ is our Savior alone \u2014 that he is our complete Savior \u2014 that all who believe are complete in him who of God is made unto us \u201c wisdom, and righteousness, and sanctification, and redemption .\u201d Cut Off \u201c I would they were even cut off which trouble you \u201d (\nv. 11). \u2014 The false teachers at Galatia charged Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]` with duplicity. They said in one place Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]` preaches circumcision (on one occasion he had Timothy circumcised as a matter of expediency), and in another [v_Act_16_3] place he opposes it. Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]` had Timothy circumcised (Acts 16:3) in hopes of being conciliatory to the Jews (It didn\u2019t work.), not to make Timothy righteous or more spiritual. The `[group_Word_Luk_1]` fact is, those who oppose the gospel of God\u2019s free, sovereign, absolute grace in Christ, claiming to be promoters of righteousness, never hesitate to slander any who preach free grace, hurling accusations against them that they know are not true. Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]`\u2019s response is simple and pointed. He asks, \u201cIf I preach circumcision (law obedience) why do your legalistic teachers relentlessly oppose me?\u201d They opposed him because the cross of Christ is now, ever has been, and ever will be an offense to work- mongers. Lost religious people do not object to the teaching that Christ is the Son of God, the Savior of sinners, the Lord our Righteousness, and our sin-atoning Substitute. They only object to that which offends their own self-righteousness \u2014 the plain revelation of the gospel that Christ is our Savior alone \u2014 that he is our complete Savior \u2014 that all who believe are complete in him who of God is made unto us \u201cwisdom, and righteousness, and sanctification, and redemption.\u201d Cut Off \u201cI would they were even cut off which trouble you\u201d ("
